      "filePath": "backend/java-admin/java-admin-infra/src/main/java/com/wshake/infra/log/TraceIdFilter.java",
      "summary": "Spring Web 过滤器实现，继承 OncePerRequestFilter：在请求入口读取或生成 traceId，写入 SLF4J MDC 与响应头 X-Trace-Id，finally 中清理 MDC。",
      "tags": ["filter", "middleware", "trace-id", "spring", "mdc", "observability"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "通过 @Order(HIGHEST_PRECEDENCE) 确保 traceId 在所有业务过滤器之前写入，try/finally 清理 MDC 是防止线程复用场景下日志串扰的关键。"
    },
